<refnamediv>
	<refname>&p;</refname>
	<refpurpose>a keyboard events sniffer</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
	<cmdsynopsis>
		<command>&p;</command>
		<arg choice='opt'><option><filename><replaceable>event-device</replaceable></filename></option></arg>
	</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection>
	<title>Description</title>
	<para>
		<command>&p;</command> displays key codes associated with keyboard events.
	</para>
</refsection>

<refsection>
	<title>Options</title>
	<para>
		<command>&p;</command> accepts the following options:
	</para>
	<variablelist>
		<varlistentry>
			<term><option><filename><replaceable>event-device</replaceable></filename></option></term>
			<listitem>
				<para>A device to listen for events. Default is <filename>/dev/input/event0</filename>.</para>
			</listitem>
		</varlistentry>
	</variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
	<title>Bugs</title>
	<para><command>input-events</command> might be a good replacement for <command>keysniff</command>.</para>
</refsection>

